Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坂 坂本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪啊 在哪啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坂本 坂本！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.57,0:00:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是丟下我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是丟下我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷者就扔一邊不管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.35,0:00:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼什麼都不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晶片的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以太心急啊我也不是有意瞞著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不就是做我的分內事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坂本你不也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互相競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事瞞著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被搶先之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會被搶先的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有三片晶片了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我誰都信不過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這晶片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我隨手撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想把它作為談判工具而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了快讓我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想見…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我不想死！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想見…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.69,0:01:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有 有誰在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了嗎坂本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於開始有幻…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚彥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:01:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候來到這島的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的 很想見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不早點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想見爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是爸爸受重傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晶片還沒集齊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很想見爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是晶片還沒….
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要集齊8片 這不可能集齊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不會這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昭子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你呆到連數都不會數了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,數數？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在有多少片晶片？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晶 晶片…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:03:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 還有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4 5…6
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7…8
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這 這不就能回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚彥 昭子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸這就回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要回去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後去找好東西吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們找個好地方痛痛快快的吃一餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起霧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且太陽也快下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜥蜴們快要醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像聽到有什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不會是蜥蜴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 這聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追蹤式？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被鎖定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好 進入射程就會爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追蹤式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有這BIM的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的話就請停手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太 後面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 在射程內
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好慘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔 求求你住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這麼殘忍的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當收集到6片晶片的時候 就是考驗你們的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說平叔 為了集齊晶片就背叛我們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那老狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼背叛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是約好一起回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你會不會就這樣不回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是被你丟棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在想這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 不要啊不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次我撐不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在把我一個人留下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我會堅持不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了平叔我們現在需要乾淨的水和毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 我們會拿很多好吃的東西回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是也逼不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我讓平叔感覺到不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明這麼害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我都沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 我不知道在什麼時候開始就
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就跟老爸做了同一樣的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一天顧著工作沒怎麼管過我的老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便離婚再隨便再婚的老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人都很自私
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只想著自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝作關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就滿足於此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對平叔也做了自己最討厭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有去照顧平叔的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 你就是這樣逃避現實的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太 龍太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒 又有BIM的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點 要快點逃離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日美子 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼 快點跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們現在進行的遊戲和BTOOOM的規則是一樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個追蹤式的性能應該也和遊戲一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不能再猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日美子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有被鎖定的人進入爆炸範圍才會爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太就由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個場景
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日美子 肯定是BTOOOM中的那個HIMIKO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔沒有移動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他肯定是藏在能看見我們的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日美子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心 追蹤式只能鎖定一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坂本 日美子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為這個遊戲 所以沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚彥 昭子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:11:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管來幾次都是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是想要殺死我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會一直進行這麼單一的攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.47,0:12:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他這手很深奧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的如此 那個BIM的目標是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔所瞄準的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是日美子妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 看破了這手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被看破了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好 我會被殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的腳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一個了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在被殺死之前 先下手為強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了柚彥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了昭子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔 我想對你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:14:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要 想要和你一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平叔一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會再讓你感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次會好好的做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你 再給我一次機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 平叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坂本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的因果報應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做了壞事的人要受到的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 坂本 日美子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:15:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想和家人團聚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚彥 昭子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 已經不想 再受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平…叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說好了一起回去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和以前那樣說一些無聊的冷笑話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泡麵只泡兩分鐘就開始吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:16:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有向平叔道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔是一開始就想要背叛我們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像伊達醫生那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔不是那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人只是個普通的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才會吃驚和懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰都會珍惜自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都想快點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓一個受了重傷的人感到絕望的感覺到極限的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔的內心已經崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是我殺死了他一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太 你也想回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 現在就想從這裡逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個狗屎的地獄裡逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以回去哦 龍太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這是剛才找到的晶片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1個是平叔的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有2個是平叔偷偷搜集的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這3個加上我們收集的晶片一共6個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我的1個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太的1個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能湊齊離開島嶼的8枚晶片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個人中有一個人死了的話 另一個人就能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 已經沒有可以回去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你改變了我這個沒有可回之處的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明在現實生活中沒有關聯的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻有一種心與心連在一起的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是虛擬的世界當中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後 到了這個島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好幾次都到生死攸關的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要崩潰的時候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我清楚的明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太就是我活下去的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果龍太能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能活下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無論自己會變成怎麼樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算變成怎麼樣都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別…別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我會想著犧牲妳讓自己回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得我是那種人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會放開妳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能放開妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是現實還是虛擬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日美子是那個HIMIKO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於察覺到了 終於見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日美子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直都想見妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日美子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還是在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻為了我盡力的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界 就是先下手為強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你的男子氣概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說又要束縛自己從而得到自我滿足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話你一生都追不上我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不再 崇拜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是體會別人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要是能明白那個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平叔就不會死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能好好的面對家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得自己是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨別人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有發生這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不會被帶到這個島嶼上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,織田 我和你不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.02,0:21:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會變成你那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再藏在我的心裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在這種地方順水推舟什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.07,0:22:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日美子 一起從這個島嶼離開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.80,0:22:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再正式的交往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.66,0:22:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和日美子一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這個地獄裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}24小時之內
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.75,0:22:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}無論怎麼樣都要在24小時之內解決
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}到了島嶼以後馬上把問題搞定 明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.01,0:23:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}我知道了 那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}喂 這件事不要告訴我們客戶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.46,0:23:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}可惡 在這種重要的時候\N島嶼上的機器出現問題
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}可惡 為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}龍太 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}學長只能幫你到這了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
